<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to FraudX</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;800&family=Space+Mono:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <style>
    /* Welcome Specific Styles */
    body { background: #FFFFFF; display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-height: 100vh; }
    .welcome-nav {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 24px 48px;
      align-items: center; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .welcome-brand {
      font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text);
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
    }
    .welcome-brand i { color: var(--accent); }
    .welcome-hero {
      flex: 1; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      padding: 60px 48px; gap: 60px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%;
    }
    .hero-text { flex: 1; }
    .hero-text h1 { font-size: 56px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .hero-text h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
    .hero-text p { font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 32px; max-width: 480px; }
    
    /* Mock Form matching illustration */
    .hero-illustration {
      flex: 1; position: relative; display: flex; justify-content: center;
    }
    .illustration-card {
      background: #FFFFFF; border: 2px solid #2C3E50; border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 32px; width: 100%; max-width: 320px; box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.1);
      text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 2;
    }
    .illustration-avatar {
      width: 64px; height: 64px; background: #2C3E50; border-radius: 50%;
      margin: 0 auto 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-size: 32px;
    }
    .illustration-input {
      width: 100%; border: 2px solid #2C3E50; padding: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px;
    }
    .illustration-btn {
      width: 100%; background: var(--accent); border: 2px solid #2C3E50; color: #2C3E50;
      padding: 12px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; transition: 0.2s;
    }
    .illustration-btn:hover { background: #45B39D; }
    
    .hacker-bg {
      position: absolute; top: -60px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: 160px; height: 160px; background: #E5E8E8; border-radius: 50%; border: 2px solid #2C3E50; z-index: 1;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .welcome-hero { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
      .hero-text p { margin: 0 auto 32px; }
    }
  </style>
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>

  <nav class="welcome-nav">
    <div class="welcome-brand">
      <div style="width: 36px; height: 36px; background: var(--accent); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; border: 2px solid #2C3E50;">
        F
      </div>
      FraudX
    </div>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px;">
      <a href="/login" class="btn btn-ghost" style="border: 2px solid #2C3E50; color: #2C3E50; font-weight: 800;">Log In</a>
      <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary" style="background: var(--accent); border: 2px solid #2C3E50; color: #2C3E50; box-shadow: none; font-weight: 800;">Sign Up</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="welcome-hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>Detect Fraud <span>Instantly.</span></h1>
      <p>Secure your transactions with intelligent, real-time ML analysis and explainable AI rules. Block bad actors before they act.</p>
      <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 16px 32px; font-size: 18px; background: var(--accent); border: 2px solid #2C3E50; color: #2C3E50; box-shadow: 6px 6px 0 rgba(44,62,80,0.1); font-weight: 800;">Get Started Now &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="hero-illustration">
      <div class="hacker-bg"></div>
      <div class="illustration-card">
        <div class="illustration-avatar">
          <i class="fas fa-user-secret"></i>
        </div>
        <form action="/login" method="GET">
          <input type="email" class="illustration-input" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
          <button type="submit" class="illustration-btn">Next</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
